N2  - Coexistence of enhanced mobile broad band (eMBB)and ultra-reliable low latency communications (URLLC) services is universal in the 5th generation mobile communication (5G) system. To increase the data rate of eMBB while ensuring the transmit requirement of URLLC, this paper proposes multi agent deep reinforcement learning based resource al location algorithms in multi-cell systems. By utilizing the advantages of multi-agent and the flexibility of time-frequency grid, the algorithms solve the nonconvex joint subchannel assignment and power allocation problem while considering co-channel interference. © 2025 IEEE.
