N2  - This paper presents a framework for team collaborative tasks based on Large Language Model (LLM) Agents. It integrates four specialized agents - task analysis, capability analysis, dynamic monitoring, and outcome integration and a four-phase workflow. The framework addresses dynamic uncertainties (e.g., resource changes, task evolution) via three core mechanisms: dynamic progress quantification, automated situation response, and prioritized conflict resolution. © 2025 IEEE.
